name: Corporal Oberk
Lore: 'Originally from Ukio. Stormtrooper assigned to search for Rebel activity on Endor. Trying to impress the commander of his biker scout detachment.',
Text: 'Adds 3 to power of any speeder bike he pilots. Once during each of your control phases, may target one opponent''s missing character at same site. Draw destiny. Add 2 if Oberk is armed with a blaster. Target captured if total destiny > ability.',
